<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; line-height: 17.12px; background: white;">Hi {!Lead.FirstName},<br></span><br>I’ve not been able to reach you since you requested a call back.<br><font face="arial" style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>It would be useful to know more about your business, so I can understand what cover you might require.<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font><font face="Arial, sans-serif">Some key benefits of our package are:</font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="font-size: 12pt;"></p><ul style="font-size: 12pt;"><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Up to £2,500 tools and equipment cover&nbsp;</b>included as standard at no extra cost (with in-van cover!)</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Next business day payout on accepted tool theft claims</b>, helping to get Britain's tradespeople back on the job faster.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>Nil excess and no hidden fees</b>&nbsp;on most professions covered, reducing out-of-pocket or unexpected costs.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>UK-based in-house specialists</b>, including easy, quick access to brokers, and rapid, responsive claims processing managed by a dedicated claims team.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif"><b>All core covers in one place</b>, wrapped into a single neat, affordable package attached to one easy payment.&nbsp;</font></li></ul><div style="font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif">However, it would be good to discuss your requirements to make sure this is the best policy for you.</font><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;Is there a good time for me to give you a call?<br></b><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>Alternatively, you can contact me on&nbsp;</font><b style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808 740</b><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">. Our office is open between the hours of 8:00am-5:30pm, Monday-Friday.&nbsp;<br></font><font face="arial"><br>I look forward to hearing from you soon.&nbsp;<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt; background-color: white;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Sales Team<br></font><font style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br>E: salesteam@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></font><font style="font-size: 12pt;">T:&nbsp;</font><font style="font-size: 12pt;">01242 808740</font></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>